01:28:41,740 --> 01:28:42,000
 Da.

1247
01:28:42,000 --> 01:28:43,160
 Zato što sam,

1248
01:28:43,160 --> 01:28:45,420
 ja išao u tom smjeru,

1249
01:28:45,420 --> 01:28:46,200
 ono,

1250
01:28:46,200 --> 01:28:47,520
 brutalne discipline.

1251
01:28:47,520 --> 01:28:49,360
 Ali ovo nije brutalna disciplina.

1252
01:28:49,360 --> 01:28:50,020
 savršeni.

1253
01:28:50,020 --> 01:28:53,100
 Možda se varam.

1254
01:28:53,100 --> 01:28:55,320
 Ja tebe

1255
01:28:55,320 --> 01:28:57,600
 uspoređujem sa sobom

1256
01:28:57,600 --> 01:28:59,540
 kakav je moj mentalni sklop.

1257
01:28:59,540 --> 01:29:01,940
 Netko kon

1258
01:29:01,940 --> 01:29:04,480
 neće pojesti,

1259
01:29:04,480 --> 01:29:05,180
 ne znam,

1260
01:29:05,180 --> 01:29:06,280
 odreko se skroz slatkog,

1261
01:29:06,280 --> 01:29:07,820
 odreko se u potpunosti alkohola,

1262
01:29:07,820 --> 01:29:09,340
 odreko se u potpunosti cigareta.

1263
01:29:09,340 --> 01:29:12,240
 Možda iz ove moje perspektive,

1264
01:29:12,240 --> 01:29:13,740
 možda ja krivo razmišljam.

1265
01:29:13,740 --> 01:29:15,360
 Izgleda kao

1266
01:29:15,360 --> 01:29:16,700
 pretjerana disciplina.

1267
01:29:19,360 --> 01:29:20,660
 Ali meni ništa ne fali.

1268
01:29:20,660 --> 01:29:21,980
 Super.

1269
01:29:21,980 --> 01:29:22,860
 Kužiš.

1270
01:29:22,860 --> 01:29:24,220
 I to je ono što smo pričali,

1271
01:29:24,220 --> 01:29:25,400
 promjena vrijednosti,

1272
01:29:25,400 --> 01:29:26,100
 jel?

1273
01:29:26,100 --> 01:29:26,720
 I promjena,

1274
01:29:26,720 --> 01:29:27,140
 znači,

1275
01:29:27,140 --> 01:29:28,480
 meni ništa

1276
01:29:28,480 --> 01:29:30,200
 ne fali.

1277
01:29:30,200 --> 01:29:31,280
 Meni ne fali cigareta,

1278
01:29:31,280 --> 01:29:32,320
 meni ne fali čokolada,

1279
01:29:32,320 --> 01:29:32,980
 meni ja nemam,

1280
01:29:32,980 --> 01:29:35,260
 meni je lakše ovako.

1281
01:29:35,260 --> 01:29:36,820
 Znači, ja sam zapravo slobodna od toga,

1282
01:29:36,820 --> 01:29:37,480
 nemam potrebu,

1283
01:29:37,480 --> 01:29:37,880
 nemam želju,

1284
01:29:37,880 --> 01:29:39,220
 ko što ti nema želju za kockanjem

1285
01:29:39,220 --> 01:29:39,780
 cijelu noć,

1286
01:29:39,780 --> 01:29:40,340
 vjerovatno.

1287
01:29:40,340 --> 01:29:41,380
 Jel da,

1288
01:29:41,380 --> 01:29:42,540
 tako ja nemam sada osjećaj,

1289
01:29:42,540 --> 01:29:43,540
 potrebu za cigaretu.

1290
01:29:44,340 --> 01:29:48,040
 Ja se ne trebam ulagati snagu

1291
01:29:48,040 --> 01:29:49,860
 da se discipliniram tu oko toga.

1292
01:29:49,860 --> 01:29:51,340
 Jednostavno nemam želju za time.

1293
01:29:51,340 --> 01:29:55,080
 To je samo onaj prestanak koji boli,

1294
01:29:55,080 --> 01:29:58,040
 a kasnije više nemaš to.

1295
01:29:58,040 --> 01:30:00,400
 I onda više čokolada nije moje odgovor,

1296
01:30:00,400 --> 01:30:01,700
 jer kad je čokolada bila moje odgovor

1297
01:30:01,700 --> 01:30:03,160
 i kad sam ja njoj dozvoljavala

1298
01:30:03,160 --> 01:30:04,100
 da bude moje odgovor,

1299
01:30:04,100 --> 01:30:04,600
 kao što smo rekli,

1300
01:30:04,600 --> 01:30:05,860
 da je tebi cigareta na kraju dana,

1301
01:30:05,860 --> 01:30:09,180
 znači, ja sam imala 25 kila više

1302
01:30:09,180 --> 01:30:10,700
 ili čak 30 sad više,

1303
01:30:10,700 --> 01:30:12,600
 znači, od sada 30 kila više.

1304
01:30:14,340 --> 01:30:17,220
 I, znači, to su stvari

1305
01:30:17,220 --> 01:30:18,540
 koje sam ja morala osvijestiti,

1306
01:30:18,540 --> 01:30:21,160
 šta zapravo čokolada znači za mene,

1307
01:30:21,160 --> 01:30:22,960
 da to nije ista informacija za mene

1308
01:30:22,960 --> 01:30:24,380
 kao što je za tebe,

1309
01:30:24,380 --> 01:30:26,000
 jer ti ne ideš čokoladu kao ja.

1310
01:30:26,000 --> 01:30:31,500
 I, znači, kad sam ja promijenila zapravo,

1311
01:30:31,500 --> 01:30:33,320
 promijenila, čitala to iskustvo,

1312
01:30:33,320 --> 01:30:34,540
 promijenila vrijednosti oko toga,

1313
01:30:34,540 --> 01:30:39,560
 ja nemam, meni ne fali to sada.

1314
01:30:39,560 --> 01:30:41,240
 Znači, to mi je baš zapravo super,

1315
01:30:41,240 --> 01:30:42,940
 jer sada to imam sve više i više,

1316
01:30:42,940 --> 01:30:44,240
 pogotovo zadnje tri mjeseca,

1317
01:30:44,240 --> 01:30:45,880
 kako sam prestala ješ čokoladu,

1318
01:30:45,880 --> 01:30:46,600
 da mi je znači, znači,

1319
01:30:46,600 --> 01:30:47,600
 znači, uopće mi ne pada na pamet,

1320
01:30:47,600 --> 01:30:48,820
 čak niti u PMS-u,

1321
01:30:48,820 --> 01:30:50,120
 gdje žene polude,

1322
01:30:50,120 --> 01:30:51,080
 i ja isto.

1323
01:30:51,080 --> 01:30:52,420
 Znači, to mi je bilo,

1324
01:30:52,420 --> 01:30:54,640
 ja prije toga isto nisam jela čokoladu,

1325
01:30:54,640 --> 01:30:55,300
 nego bi jela, znači,

1326
01:30:55,300 --> 01:30:56,240
 kad bi bila u PMS-u,

1327
01:30:56,240 --> 01:30:57,340
 recimo, oko tih dana,

1328
01:30:57,340 --> 01:30:59,480
 bi mi se tu desio nekakav kreš,

1329
01:30:59,480 --> 01:31:01,500
 onda bi se trudila da ne bude prevelik kreš.

1330
01:31:01,740 --> 01:31:04,360
 To sam ja uspjela kao trenerica tada sebi napraviti,

1331
01:31:04,360 --> 01:31:05,940
 i bilo okej, ništa strašna,

1332
01:31:05,940 --> 01:31:06,700
 sam to hendlala,

1333
01:31:06,700 --> 01:31:07,760
 i onda sam kao donijela,

1334
01:31:07,760 --> 01:31:09,220
 ajde da mi probati tu odluku,

1335
01:31:09,220 --> 01:31:10,760
 i ja kako sam nju odluku donijela,

1336
01:31:10,760 --> 01:31:11,480
 i kako sam prestala,

1337
01:31:11,480 --> 01:31:12,960
 meni ništa ne fali,

1338
01:31:12,960 --> 01:31:13,880
 ja sam sretna,

1339
01:31:14,040 --> 01:31:14,500
 Vinko,

1340
01:31:14,500 --> 01:31:16,040
 ja sam sretnija,

1341
01:31:16,040 --> 01:31:17,340
 znači,

1342
01:31:17,340 --> 01:31:19,220
 slobodna sam,

1343
01:31:19,220 --> 01:31:20,280
 od te želje,

1344
01:31:20,280 --> 01:31:21,340
 hoću li neću li,

1345
01:31:21,340 --> 01:31:21,940
 hoću li jedno,

1346
01:31:21,940 --> 01:31:22,540
 hoću li dvije,

1347
01:31:22,540 --> 01:31:23,480
 ne bi trebala,

1348
01:31:23,480 --> 01:31:24,640
 ajde sutra ću,

1349
01:31:24,640 --> 01:31:26,220
 ajde i preko sutra ću,

1350
01:31:26,220 --> 01:31:27,280
 o sad imam dva za redom,

1351
01:31:27,280 --> 01:31:27,900
 ne bi više smijela,

1352
01:31:27,900 --> 01:31:28,360
 znači,

1353
01:31:28,360 --> 01:31:30,160
 cijelo to bunilo u glavi,

1354
01:31:30,160 --> 01:31:31,240
 ja ga nemam,

1355
01:31:31,240 --> 01:31:32,160
 više,

1356
01:31:32,160 --> 01:31:33,380
 ja sam slobodna,

1357
01:31:33,380 --> 01:31:33,860
 meni,

1358
01:31:33,860 --> 01:31:35,880
 kožiš?

1359
01:31:35,880 --> 01:31:38,520
 Razumijem,

1360
01:31:38,520 --> 01:31:40,700
 razumijem,

1361
01:31:40,700 --> 01:31:42,780
 znaš zašto te razumijem,

1362
01:31:42,780 --> 01:31:43,460
 zato što sam,

1363
01:31:44,040 --> 01:31:46,140
 i sam bio u trenucima,

1364
01:31:46,140 --> 01:31:47,660
 kad nisam pušio,

1365
01:31:47,660 --> 01:31:51,100
 kad nisam imao to kompulzivno,

1366
01:31:51,100 --> 01:31:52,080
 nekako ponašanje,

1367
01:31:52,080 --> 01:31:55,300
 i zapravo sam se osjećao puno slobodnije,

1368
01:31:55,300 --> 01:31:56,600
 tada.

1369
01:31:56,600 --> 01:31:57,680
 Da.

1370
01:31:57,680 --> 01:31:59,020
 I sad tebi neko kaže,

1371
01:31:59,020 --> 01:32:00,120
 ti si discipliniran kako,

1372
01:32:00,120 --> 01:32:01,680
 ne, ti si slobodan.

1373
01:32:01,680 --> 01:32:04,520
 I kužiš kako imamo pogrešnu priču,

1374
01:32:04,520 --> 01:32:05,740
 oko toga.

1375
01:32:05,740 --> 01:32:07,960
 I to je priča koju si pričamo,

1376
01:32:07,960 --> 01:32:09,260
 i ako si pričamo tu priču,

1377
01:32:09,260 --> 01:32:11,340
 ne možemo prestati raditi to ponašanje,

1378
01:32:11,340 --> 01:32:12,500
 jer si pričamo krivu priču,

1379
01:32:12,500 --> 01:32:13,100
 jer ti kažeš,

1380
01:32:13,380 --> 01:32:13,960
 tebi je teško,

1381
01:32:13,960 --> 01:32:14,920
 ti se odričeš,

1382
01:32:14,920 --> 01:32:16,100
 a ja se nagrađujem.

1383
01:32:16,100 --> 01:32:16,480
 Ne,

1384
01:32:16,480 --> 01:32:17,520
 ti se truješ,

1385
01:32:17,520 --> 01:32:18,240
 oprosti sad,

1386
01:32:18,240 --> 01:32:19,060
 ja sam isto pušila,

1387
01:32:19,060 --> 01:32:19,860
 ne mislim to,

1388
01:32:19,860 --> 01:32:21,920
 ali zapravo kad bi pogledali činjenice,

1389
01:32:21,920 --> 01:32:22,280
 znači,

1390
01:32:22,280 --> 01:32:23,860
 uopće nemam stava o tome,

1391
01:32:23,860 --> 01:32:24,640
 meni je to nevažno,

1392
01:32:24,640 --> 01:32:25,480
 ali je,

1393
01:32:25,480 --> 01:32:26,740
 kad bi pogledali činjenice,

1394
01:32:26,740 --> 01:32:27,580
 ili kao ja,

1395
01:32:27,580 --> 01:32:28,480
 kao,

1396
01:32:28,480 --> 01:32:29,200
 recimo,

1397
01:32:29,200 --> 01:32:30,300
 uzeti ću sebe za primjer,

1398
01:32:30,300 --> 01:32:31,640
 ja kada sam,

1399
01:32:31,640 --> 01:32:33,000
 ja kao volim pušenje,

1400
01:32:33,000 --> 01:32:34,540
 meni nije bilo do prestanka pušenje,

1401
01:32:34,540 --> 01:32:35,780
 ili ja volim čokoladu,

1402
01:32:35,780 --> 01:32:37,100
 halo,

1403
01:32:37,220 --> 01:32:39,060
 ti nemaš kontrolu nad čokoladom,

1404
01:32:39,060 --> 01:32:39,800
 Danijela,

1405
01:32:39,800 --> 01:32:40,460
 znači,

1406
01:32:40,460 --> 01:32:41,880
 tvoje tijelo nije zdravo,

1407
01:32:41,880 --> 01:32:42,700
 ti jedeš previše,

1408
01:32:42,700 --> 01:32:43,000
 znači,

1409
01:32:43,000 --> 01:32:44,840
 ideš konstantno joj joj,

1410
01:32:44,840 --> 01:32:45,400
 idemo vamo,

1411
01:32:45,400 --> 01:32:45,920
 pa idemo nad,

1412
01:32:45,920 --> 01:32:46,220
 znači,

1413
01:32:46,220 --> 01:32:47,540
 ali pričamo tu priču,

1414
01:32:47,540 --> 01:32:47,960
 ja kao,

1415
01:32:47,960 --> 01:32:49,640
 moje klijenti se to znaju pričati,

1416
01:32:49,640 --> 01:32:49,920
 kao,

1417
01:32:49,920 --> 01:32:50,640
 jao,

1418
01:32:50,640 --> 01:32:51,760
 jadna ja,

1419
01:32:52,300 --> 01:32:54,240
 kakav je to život,

1420
01:32:54,240 --> 01:32:54,660
 halo,

1421
01:32:54,660 --> 01:32:55,120
 kakav je život,

1422
01:32:55,120 --> 01:32:56,620
 imaš 40 kila viška,

1423
01:32:56,620 --> 01:32:57,320
 mislim,

1424
01:32:57,320 --> 01:32:59,600
 zluči skroz grubo,

1425
01:32:59,600 --> 01:33:02,060
 ali imaš 40 kila viška,

1426
01:33:02,060 --> 01:33:03,920
 čokolada nije za tebe,

1427
01:33:03,920 --> 01:33:06,140
 jer ti konstantno plaćaš programe,

1428
01:33:06,140 --> 01:33:07,300
 plaćaš psihologa,

1429
01:33:07,300 --> 01:33:07,980
 nutricioniste,

1430
01:33:07,980 --> 01:33:10,100
 po cijelu godinu pokušavaš,

1431
01:33:10,100 --> 01:33:11,480
 smršaviti,

1432
01:33:11,480 --> 01:33:11,700
 znači,

1433
01:33:11,700 --> 01:33:13,140
 ta čokolada te ima,

1434
01:33:13,140 --> 01:33:14,140
 kriva priča je,

1435
01:33:14,140 --> 01:33:14,480
 uživanje,

1436
01:33:14,480 --> 01:33:15,760
 jednom se živi to,

1437
01:33:15,760 --> 01:33:16,160
 ne,

1438
01:33:16,160 --> 01:33:17,580
 nego ti umireš,

1439
01:33:17,580 --> 01:33:18,560
 užas,

1440
01:33:18,560 --> 01:33:19,960
 ne mogu vjerati sam sad sve ovo rekla,

1441
01:33:19,960 --> 01:33:21,200
 ali je istina,

1442
01:33:21,600 --> 01:33:21,980
 zapravo,

1443
01:33:21,980 --> 01:33:23,680
 i mi sebi pričamo tu priču,

1444
01:33:23,680 --> 01:33:24,060
 da je kao,

1445
01:33:24,060 --> 01:33:25,600
 jo, šta je život bez čokolade,

1446
01:33:25,600 --> 01:33:26,520
 halo, ne,

1447
01:33:26,520 --> 01:33:28,140
 fakt tu čokoladu,

1448
01:33:28,140 --> 01:33:31,740
 ali je zato što imamo pogrešnu priču,

1449
01:33:31,740 --> 01:33:32,560
 sebi pričamo,

1450
01:33:32,560 --> 01:33:34,040
 ne možemo promijeniti,

1451
01:33:34,040 --> 01:33:36,240
 donijeti tu odluku i promijeniti tu naviku.

1452
01:33:36,240 --> 01:33:39,440
 Užas, što sam ja rekla.

1453
01:33:39,440 --> 01:33:43,180
 Užas.

1454
01:33:43,180 --> 01:33:45,100
 Nije baš i fora.

1455
01:33:45,100 --> 01:33:49,100
 Šta stoji iza tog imena brenda,

1456
01:33:49,100 --> 01:33:51,300
 Anansi?

1457
01:33:51,400 --> 01:33:58,140
 Anansi je pauk,

1458
01:33:58,140 --> 01:33:59,440
 znači,

1459
01:33:59,440 --> 01:34:00,760
 meni je to bio moj izlaz,

1460
01:34:00,760 --> 01:34:01,400
 zapravo,

1461
01:34:01,400 --> 01:34:02,860
 dosta povezano sa,

1462
01:34:02,860 --> 01:34:04,640
 to mojom debljinom,

1463
01:34:04,640 --> 01:34:06,940
 impostor sindromom,

1464
01:34:06,940 --> 01:34:09,300
 gdje mi je Anansi,

1465
01:34:10,400 --> 01:34:12,120
 ne znam šta je Anansi uvijek.

1466
01:34:12,120 --> 01:34:15,840
 Znači, on je iz afričkih narodnih priča,

1467
01:34:15,840 --> 01:34:16,660
 pauk,

1468
01:34:16,660 --> 01:34:20,360
 koji skuplja mudrosti po svijetu

1469
01:34:20,360 --> 01:34:23,100
 i dijeli ih sa ostalim paukovima.

1470
01:34:25,100 --> 01:34:26,840
 i to je...

1471
01:34:26,840 --> 01:34:32,240
 nekako mi se činilo,

1472
01:34:32,240 --> 01:34:32,760
 znači,

1473
01:34:33,260 --> 01:34:37,060
 da onda ja imam pravo da na taj način,

1474
01:34:37,060 --> 01:34:40,300
 jer nisam imala sam osjećaj da nemam pravo da govorim,

1475
01:34:41,860 --> 01:34:43,120
 da se pojavljamo u svome poslu,

1476
01:34:43,120 --> 01:34:44,460
 da govorimo o svome poslu,

1477
01:34:44,460 --> 01:34:45,420
 da govorimo o tome,

1478
01:34:45,420 --> 01:34:47,200
 da ja išta nešto to znam,

1479
01:34:47,200 --> 01:34:48,400
 pošto nemam rezultat,

1480
01:34:48,400 --> 01:34:49,860
 a i ne znam sve što bi trebalo.

1481
01:34:49,860 --> 01:34:53,880
 To sam imala jako, jako, jako izraženu tu perfekcionističku crtu tada,

1482
01:34:53,880 --> 01:34:55,440
 ono što smo pričali,

1483
01:34:55,440 --> 01:34:57,640
 što ja sad više niti ne osjećam da je toliko imam,

1484
01:34:58,240 --> 01:35:01,180
 ali tada me je imala toliko da ja nisam imala pravo,

1485
01:35:01,180 --> 01:35:02,540
 zato što ne znam sve o tome,

1486
01:35:02,540 --> 01:35:03,880
 da pričam išta o toga,

1487
01:35:03,880 --> 01:35:06,060
 pogotovo što nemam rezultat što sam debela trenerica,

1488
01:35:06,060 --> 01:35:06,340
 znaš.

1489
01:35:06,340 --> 01:35:09,960
 I onda mi je ta priča o anansiju dala,

1490
01:35:09,960 --> 01:35:14,000
 kao da mi je dala dozvolu za govor,

1491
01:35:14,000 --> 01:35:14,840
 dozvolu za rad,

1492
01:35:14,840 --> 01:35:16,020
 dozvolu za dijeljanje,

1493
01:35:16,020 --> 01:35:18,900
 jer ja nisam morala nešto znati i izmisliti,

1494
01:35:18,900 --> 01:35:21,660
 ja sam mogla učiti od drugih ljudi

1495
01:35:21,660 --> 01:35:23,480
 i prenositi to znanje drugima.

1496
01:35:23,480 --> 01:35:27,840
 Zadnje pitanje.

1497
01:35:28,240 --> 01:35:31,280
 Koja je tvoja definicija uspjeha?

1498
01:35:31,280 --> 01:35:34,240
 Uspjeha?

